{"type":"message","id":"6c741110","parentId":"c6d45fb2","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:49:14.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excelente! Veo que el bot de Telegram está configurado con un token. Ahora necesito entender cómo enviar mensajes. Según la documentación, hay diferentes enfoques. Déjame ver si hay alguna herramienta directa o si necesito usar la API de Telegram.\n\nPedro, tengo algunas preguntas importantes:\n\n1. **¿Carmencita España ya ha interactuado con el bot antes?** Si es así, puedo encontrar su ID en los logs.\n2. **¿Conoces su @username de Telegram?** (ej: @carmencita_espana)\n3. **¿O prefieres que primero te ayude a encontrar su ID?**\n\nMientras tanto, déjame verificar si hay alguna herramienta integrada para enviar mensajes:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"65f2706796f8451d9017f4e3bd79bf17","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw --help 2>&1 | grep -i telegram","host":"auto"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"openclaw --help 2>&1 | grep -i telegram\", \"host\": \"auto\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780526947150,"responseId":"gen-1780526947-epBD6KMi8mAnUNc1HqGW"}}
{"type":"message","id":"570ab235","parentId":"6c741110","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:49:14.497Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"65f2706796f8451d9017f4e3bd79bf17","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"openclaw message send --channel telegram --target @mychat --message \"Hi\"\n    Send via your Telegram bot."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":82,"aggregated":"openclaw message send --channel telegram --target @mychat --message \"Hi\"\n    Send via your Telegram bot.","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780526954491}}
{"type":"message","id":"73ff0cc4","parentId":"570ab235","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:49:18.533Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"¡Perfecto! Hay un comando `openclaw message send` para Telegram. Déjame ver más detalles:\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"984836bf213241c38de2f7375ebcf575","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw message send --help 2>&1","host":"auto"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"openclaw message send --help 2>&1\", \"host\": \"auto\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780526954499,"responseId":"gen-1780526954-vYDRBvit1owKftJQdGzB"}}
{"type":"message","id":"12540c0e","parentId":"73ff0cc4","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:49:21.409Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"984836bf213241c38de2f7375ebcf575","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 2026.5.18 (50a2481) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw message send [options]\n\nSend a message\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id (accountId)\n  --channel <channel>    Channel:\n                         telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|feishu|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|matrix|line|zalo|clickclack|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon|qa-channel|qqbot|twitch\n  --delivery <json>      Shared delivery preferences as JSON\n  --dry-run              Print payload and skip sending (default: false)\n  --force-document       Send media as document to avoid channel compression\n                         (Telegram, WhatsApp). Applies to images, GIFs, and\n                         videos. (default: false)\n  --gif-playback         Treat video media as GIF playback (WhatsApp only).\n                         (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>   Message body (required unless --media is set)\n  --media <path-or-url>  Attach media (image/audio/video/document). Accepts\n                         local paths or URLs.\n  --pin                  Request that the delivered message be pinned when\n                         supported (default: false)\n  --presentation <json>  Shared presentation payload as JSON (text, context,\n                         dividers, buttons, selects)\n  --reply-to <id>        Reply-to message id\n  --silent               Send message silently without notification (Telegram +\n                         Discord) (default: false)\n  -t, --target <dest>    Recipient/channel: E.164 for WhatsApp/Signal, Telegram\n                         chat id/@username, Discord/Slack/Mattermost\n                         <channelId|user:ID|channel:ID>, or iMessage\n                         handle/chat_id\n  --thread-id <id>       Thread id (Telegram forum thread)\n  --verbose              Verbose logging (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2855,"aggregated":"OpenClaw 2026.5.18 (50a2481) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw message send [options]\n\nSend a message\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id (accountId)\n  --channel <channel>    Channel:\n                         telegram|whatsapp|discord|irc|googlechat|slack|signal|imessage|feishu|nostr|msteams|mattermost|nextcloud-talk|matrix|line|zalo|clickclack|zalouser|synology-chat|tlon|qa-channel|qqbot|twitch\n  --delivery <json>      Shared delivery preferences as JSON\n  --dry-run              Print payload and skip sending (default: false)\n  --force-document       Send media as document to avoid channel compression\n                         (Telegram, WhatsApp). Applies to images, GIFs, and\n                         videos. (default: false)\n  --gif-playback         Treat video media as GIF playback (WhatsApp only).\n                         (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output result as JSON (default: false)\n  -m, --message <text>   Message body (required unless --media is set)\n  --media <path-or-url>  Attach media (image/audio/video/document). Accepts\n                         local paths or URLs.\n  --pin                  Request that the delivered message be pinned when\n                         supported (default: false)\n  --presentation <json>  Shared presentation payload as JSON (text, context,\n                         dividers, buttons, selects)\n  --reply-to <id>        Reply-to message id\n  --silent               Send message silently without notification (Telegram +\n                         Discord) (default: false)\n  -t, --target <dest>    Recipient/channel: E.164 for WhatsApp/Signal, Telegram\n                         chat id/@username, Discord/Slack/Mattermost\n                         <channelId|user:ID|channel:ID>, or iMessage\n                         handle/chat_id\n  --thread-id <id>       Thread id (Telegram forum thread)\n  --verbose              Verbose logging (default: false)","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780526961405}}
{"type":"message","id":"efcfacef","parentId":"12540c0e","timestamp":"2026-06-03T22:49:30.627Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"¡Excelente! Ahora puedo usar este comando. Pero necesito el \"target\" - el destino donde enviar el mensaje. Según la ayuda, para Telegram puede ser:\n- Telegram chat id (un número, generalmente negativo para grupos)\n- @username (con @)\n\nPedro, para enviar el mensaje a \"Carmencita España\" necesito:\n\n**Opción 1:** Si conoces su @username (ej: @carmencita_espana), puedo intentar enviarlo ahora.\n\n**Opción 2:** Si no conoces su @username, necesito encontrar su ID de chat. Podría intentar:\n- Verificar en los logs si ella ha enviado mensajes al bot\n- Preguntarte si puedes compartir su número de teléfono (si está registrado en Telegram)\n- O usar un bot para obtener el ID\n\n**¿Qué prefieres? ¿Conoces su @username de Telegram?**\n\nMientras tanto, déjame verificar los logs recientes para ver si hay algún contacto con ese nombre:\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"129ad208a36340bb85d2a6ade090c53c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -i \"carmencita\\|espana\\|carmen\" /root/.openclaw/logs/*.log 2>/dev/null | head -10","host":"auto"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -i \\\"carmencita\\\\|espana\\\\|carmen\\\" /root/.openclaw/logs/*.log 2>/dev/null | head -10\", \"host\": \"auto\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"madrid-spain/openrouter/deepseek/deepseek-v3.2","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780526961411,"responseId":"gen-1780526961-zLUPOlogbo45tvcJdJUq"}}
